yingyinNormal.en: She made me baby-proof the whole hotel. Someone's over-protective.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她让我把整个酒店都做防护了，某人过分保护了。

yingyinNormal.en: The use of illegal protective gel is cause for elimination. What!
yingyinNormal.zh: 因使用非法的保护凝胶而遭到淘汰。什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, but he's very protective of me so you'd better watch yourself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他很保护我，你最好小心一点。

yingyinNormal.en: A single Yellowjacket offers the user unlimited influence to carry out protective actions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一件黄蜂战衣使用者就可以拥有无限潜能以实施防御举措。

yingyinNormal.en: That's different. First of all, we're not engaged; and second, Indian parents are very protective of their children.
yingyinNormal.zh: 呃，这不一样，首先，我们还没订婚，其次，印度父母都对孩子很不放心的。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, if you are so protective of the scientific method, perhaps we should use the next five weeks to finish what we started.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你对科学方法的保护欲这么强，也许我们应该用接下来五周时间做完我们已经开始做的事。

yingyinNormal.en: Ross, look, I know I've been giving you a lot of jabs and it's partly because I'm very protective of Lizzie, and partly because well, they just keep coming to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 罗斯，我知道我一直找你麻烦，因为我很保护丽莎，而且你的缺点实在很多。
